# Managed by Ansible — generic/smb-mount role. Do not edit by hand.
# Caps the LaunchDaemon log (smb-mount-fixup) at 100KB and keeps 3
# bzip2'd archives. Runs via the system newsyslog cron — no extra
# daemon. Insurance against a runaway logging loop if the daemon
# ever gets KeepAlive or a watchpath added.
# Format: logfilename                          owner:group  mode count size when flags
{{ smb_mount_fixup_log }} root:wheel 644 3 100 * J
